<body>
<div><head>一</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_001-1a.2">曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_001-1a.3">「明主有三懼，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_001-1a.4">一曰<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_001-1a.5">｛不｝聞其過；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_001-1a.6">二曰得志□<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_001-1a.7">如恐不能行<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>二</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_002-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_002-1a" ed="CHANT" n="002-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_002-1a.2">子貢問孔子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_002-1a.3">「賜為人下，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_002-1a.4">如不知為<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_002-1a.5">下。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_002-1a.6">孔子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_002-1a.7">「為人下者其猶士乎？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_002-1a.8">種<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_002-1a.9">得五谷焉，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_002-1a.10">撅之得甘泉焉，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_002-1a.11">草木植<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_002-1a.12">禽獸伏焉，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_002-1a.13">生人立焉，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_002-1a.14">死人入焉。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_002-1a.15">多<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_002-1a.16">□其言。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_002-1a.17">為人下者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_002-1a.18">其猶土乎？<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>三</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_003-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_003-1a" ed="CHANT" n="003-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_003-1a.2">曾折｛援｝木擊曾子□<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_003-1a.3">者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_003-1a.4">參得罪夫子夫子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_003-1a.5">得毋病乎退而就<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_003-1a.6">曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_003-1a.7">參來勿內也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_003-1a.8">曾子自<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_003-1a.9">之未嘗可得也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_003-1a.10">小箠則待笞，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_003-1a.11">大<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_003-1a.12">□怒立，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_003-1a.13">而不去殺身以□父□<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_003-1a.14">之民與<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_003-1a.15">殺天子之民者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_003-1a.16">其罪<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>四</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_004-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_004-1a" ed="CHANT" n="004-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_004-1a.2">伐陳，西門□，因使其降民修之□<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_004-1a.3">二人□<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_004-1a.4">子曰丘也<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>五</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_005-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_005-1a" ed="CHANT" n="005-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_005-1a.2">桓公謂管仲曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_005-1a.3">「諸｛侯｝<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_005-1a.4">｛管｝仲對｛曰｝：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_005-1a.5">不出境。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_005-1a.6">桓公<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_005-1a.7">今予不道<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_005-1a.8">割燕君之所至如。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_005-1a.9">｛諸｝<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>六</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_006-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_006-1a" ed="CHANT" n="006-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_006-1a.2">□漁者曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_006-1a.3">「天暑而得｛鬻｝之不□，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_006-1a.4">思<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_006-1a.5">將祭之□乎？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_006-1a.6">孔子曰<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>七</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_007-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_007-1a" ed="CHANT" n="007-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_007-1a.2">閑處，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_007-1a.3">喟然嘆曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_007-1a.4">「銅鞮柏華<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_007-1a.5">者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_007-1a.6">周公旦攝天下之｛政｝，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_007-1a.7">也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_007-1a.8">夫有道乃無下於天下｛哉｝！<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>八</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_008-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_008-1a" ed="CHANT" n="008-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_008-1a.2">於大廟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_008-1a.3">右階之前，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_008-1a.4">有｛銅｝<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_008-1a.5">□其口，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_008-1a.6">如銘其背曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_008-1a.7">「戒之戒之<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_008-1a.8">之為人也多，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_008-1a.9">言多過，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_008-1a.10">多事多患也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>九</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_009-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_009-1a" ed="CHANT" n="009-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_009-1a.2">齊景公問子貢曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_009-1a.3">「子誰師<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_009-1a.4">乎。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_009-1a.5">子貢<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_009-1a.6">也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_009-1a.7">公曰<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_009-1a.8">子知其聖<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_009-1a.9">長，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_009-1a.10">皆曰高，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_009-1a.11">高幾何，<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>十</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_010-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_010-1a" ed="CHANT" n="010-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_010-1a.2">襄子問仲尼曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_010-1a.3">「先生行見<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_010-1a.4">意先生之道固不通乎？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_010-1a.5">仲<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_010-1a.6">□襄子見子路曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_010-1a.7">「吾嘗問先生，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_010-1a.8">先生不□<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_010-1a.9">對即隱也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_010-1a.10">隱<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_010-1a.11">安得為仁者<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_010-1a.12">不知□得為聖？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_010-1a.13">子路曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_010-1a.14">「今□天下<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_010-1a.15">之鳴鐘如冲之以梃<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>十一</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_011-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_011-1a" ed="CHANT" n="011-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_011-1a.2">子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_011-1a.3">「犢主澤鳴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_011-1a.4">晉國之賢□<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_011-1a.5">聞君子重傷□<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>十二</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_012-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_012-1a" ed="CHANT" n="012-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_012-1a.2">子匡，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_012-1a.3">簡子欲殺陽虎，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_012-1a.4">孔子｛似｝之<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_012-1a.5">□□孔子。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_012-1a.6">孔子□舍。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_012-1a.7">子路怒奮｛戟｝欲下。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_012-1a.8">子止之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_012-1a.9">「何仁義之不意□□<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_012-1a.10">詩書不習，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_012-1a.11">禮樂不修，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_012-1a.12">則<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_012-1a.13">是丘之罪<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_012-1a.14">陽虎如為陽虎，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_012-1a.15">則是非丘□<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>十三</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_013-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_013-1a" ed="CHANT" n="013-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_013-1a.2">君子道四，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_013-1a.3">彊於行，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_013-1a.4">弱於辭□<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>十四</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_014-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_014-1a" ed="CHANT" n="014-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_014-1a.2">何？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_014-1a.3">仲尼曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_014-1a.4">「新交取親<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>十五</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_015-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_015-1a" ed="CHANT" n="015-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_015-1a.2">路行辭於孔<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_015-1a.3">孔子<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_015-1a.4">孔子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_015-1a.5">「贈若以車乎？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_015-1a.6">言乎？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_015-1a.7">子路請以言，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_015-1a.8">孔子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_015-1a.9">「不彊不<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>十六</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_016-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_016-1a" ed="CHANT" n="016-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_016-1a.2">曾子有疾，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_016-1a.3">公猛義往問之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_016-1a.4">曾子言曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_016-1a.5">「<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_016-1a.6">鳥之將死也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_016-1a.7">必有悲聲；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_016-1a.8">君子將卒也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_016-1a.9">也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_016-1a.10">曾子□<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_016-1a.11">立志則貪欲之心止<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_016-1a.12">則怠隋慢易之節止。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_016-1a.13">君子<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>十七</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_017-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_017-1a" ed="CHANT" n="017-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_017-1a.2">張罔者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_017-1a.3">四面張，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_017-1a.4">如祝之□<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_017-1a.5">□□者四方來者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_017-1a.6">皆麗<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_017-1a.7">予。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_017-1a.8">欲左者左欲右者右欲高者高<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_017-1a.9">□者下，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_017-1a.10">請受其犯命者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_017-1a.11">｛漢｝陭之□，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_017-1a.12">之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_017-1a.13">「湯之德及禽獸矣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_017-1a.14">故吾<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_017-1a.15">四十余國來服<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>十八</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_018-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_018-1a" ed="CHANT" n="018-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_018-1a.2">王居鄗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_018-1a.3">使人治池得人<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_018-1a.4">曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_018-1a.5">「殯之。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_018-1a.6">吏曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_018-1a.7">「此毋主矣。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_018-1a.8">文王曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_018-1a.9">「□<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_018-1a.10">一家之主也；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_018-1a.11">長一國者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_018-1a.12">國<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_018-1a.13">｛也｝。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_018-1a.14">長天下者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_018-1a.15">天下<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_018-1a.16">之人聞之□<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>十九</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a" ed="CHANT" n="019-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.2">崔子□□<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.3">□公劫晏子於&amp;CH-0F22A5;上曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.4">「子□<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.5">我將舍子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.6">子不我與，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.7">將殺子□□□<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.8">可之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.9">晏子劫之<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.10">□其志，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.11">非恿也；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.12">□｛也｝，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.13">以<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.14">非義也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.15">子何不誰之？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.16">崔<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.17">子舍之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.18">晏子<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.19">□，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.20">其僕將馳，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.21">晏子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.22">「□之<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_019-1a.23">按之成節<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>二十</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_020-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_020-1a" ed="CHANT" n="020-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_020-1a.2">子屈廬曰<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_020-1a.3">與我，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_020-1a.4">將舍子；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_020-1a.5">子不我與，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_020-1a.6">將殺子。」屈｛廬｝<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_020-1a.7">乎？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_020-1a.8">且吾聞<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_020-1a.9">□臨死不怒。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_020-1a.10">夫人臣□<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_020-1a.11">勝乃內其劍<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>二十一</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_021-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_021-1a" ed="CHANT" n="021-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_021-1a.2">於魯}<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_021-1a.3">□□如趨受｛玉｝<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_021-1a.4">臣敢不趨乎君之<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_021-1a.5">受敝卑，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_021-1a.6">臣敢<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>二十二</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_022-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_022-1a" ed="CHANT" n="022-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_022-1a.2">故人主孝，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_022-1a.3">則名<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_022-1a.4">天下譽矣；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_022-1a.5">人臣孝則事君忠，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_022-1a.6">處<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_022-1a.7">置之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_022-1a.8">子不敢撅也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_022-1a.9">父母全之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_022-1a.10">子不敢<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_022-1a.11">父母全而生之<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>二十三</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_023-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_023-1a" ed="CHANT" n="023-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_023-1a.2">子惡言不出於口，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_023-1a.3">蕠言不反於己□<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>二十四</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_024-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_024-1a" ed="CHANT" n="024-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_024-1a.2">膚，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_024-1a.3">受諸父母，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_024-1a.4">曾子<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_024-1a.5">何謂身體髮膚，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_024-1a.6">弗敢毀傷？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_024-1a.7">曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_024-1a.8">「樂正子<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_024-1a.9">毀傷，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_024-1a.10">父不子也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_024-1a.11">士不友也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_024-1a.12">□□<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_024-1a.13">尊榮無懮子道，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_024-1a.14">如此可謂孝<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_024-1a.15">□□教之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_024-1a.16">所由曰孝□經□□<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_024-1a.17">之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_024-1a.18">且夫為人子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_024-1a.19">親死然後事<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>二十五</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_025-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_025-1a" ed="CHANT" n="025-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_025-1a.2">□也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_025-1a.3">子路曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_025-1a.4">「然。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_025-1a.5">願聞成人。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_025-1a.6">孔子曰<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_025-1a.7">何以為成人哉？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_025-1a.8">子路曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_025-1a.9">「由□<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_025-1a.10">孔子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_025-1a.11">「由其可以<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>二十六</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_026-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_026-1a" ed="CHANT" n="026-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_026-1a.2">林放問禮<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
<div><head>二十七</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_027-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_027-1a" ed="CHANT" n="027-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4103_CHANT_027-1a.2">問□告朔<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
